text: Mauro Jagodnich (born 11 July 1967) is an Italian rower. He competed in the men's double sculls event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Italian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Italy Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
